	"Total improvement in in-game time: 0:06::01. Due to the improved transition between Scrap Brain Zones 2 and 3, the total real-time improvement is of almost 13 seconds.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The times given are the in-game timer values. The value after the final colon indicates the in-game frame counter, and is restricted to the 0-59 range. It is updated every frame (except during lag frames), and increments the in-game second when resetting to zero.
	$LF
]div
