[h4 id=LabyrinthZone3 
	" Labyrinth Zone 3
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"This is an improvement that should have been included in the previous movie; I have no idea why it isn't there. I noticed the omission when I was splicing in the new tricks. A more optimized exit from the last wall gives the entire improvement.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=StarLightZone1 
	" Star Light Zone 1
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Using the glitch found by Romulo the Brazillian, which is in the 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=latest Sonic run|href=/2457S)
	". Due to spindashes in the previous version of the movie, the glitch isn't as effective for Tails as it is for Sonic.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=StarLightZone2 
	" Star Light Zone 2
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Using the glitch found by Romulo the Brazillian, which GGG managed to reproduce and I slightly improved, this level is now sub-10 seconds.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=StarLightZone3 
	" Star Light Zone 3
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Using the glitch found by Romulo the Brazillian, which is in the 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=latest Sonic run|href=/2457S)
	", leads to a rather large improvement on the level -- 5 seconds and 9 frames.
	$LF
]div
